            <abstract id="ref37" label="Abstract">This collection contains photographs, memorabilia, and correspondence relating to John Ricci's tenure as a professor of chemistry at New York University.</abstract>
        </did>
        <arrangement id="ref10">
            <head>Arrangement</head>
            <p>The collection consists of two series, in which items are arranged chronologically. Series I consists of photos, memorabilia and correspondence related to Ricci's student days and teaching career at the University. Series II consists of photos and related correspondence given to Ricci from students on his retirement.</p>
        </arrangement>
